# Currency Converter 💱

A simple and elegant currency converter app built with **Flutter**. This app allows users to convert **USD to BDT** with a clean and modern UI.

## 🚀 Features
- 🔄 Convert USD to BDT in real time  
- 🎨 Minimalist and smart UI design  
- ⚡ Smooth user experience with Cupertino & Material widgets  
- 🌐 Works offline (No internet required)  
- 🚀 Lightweight and fast  

